- When available, use `AskUserQuestion` for manual or human-only blockers rather than silently proceeding
- Subagent caveat: subagents cannot use `AskUserQuestion` or share the parent's task list. When running as a subagent, capture any manual steps or verification items in your output so the parent agent can surface them
